OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FOver the past two years, ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian has been reporting on the
OL,8,Fchronic lack of driving tests
OL,9,Favailable in the Thames Valley and the
OL,10,Fsituation doesn't appear to be getting
OL,11,Fmuch better.
OL,13,FIn fact, Newbury now has one of the
OL,14,Flongest waits for a test in the
OL,15,Fcountry.
OL,17,FAccording to local MP, Lee Dillon, the
OL,18,Fcurrent wait in Newbury is nearly a
OL,19,Fyear. Nationally, it's around four and
OL,20,Fa half months.
