OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FThe backlog emerged during the
OL,7,Fpandemic and now there's a huge drive
OL,8,Fto recruit more examiners.
OL,10,F17-year-old Sophie Carter, from
OL,11,FChieveley, is desperate to pass her
OL,12,Fdriving test.
OL,14,FShe lives in the countryside and
OL,15,Fcurrently relies on lifts to get to
OL,16,Fschool and her part time job.
OL,18,FA stress-induced error caused her to
OL,19,Ffail her first test and now she's
OL,20,Ffacing an agonising wait to rebook.
