OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FSophie said: "It took me seven months
OL,7,Fto get my first test and obviously
OL,8,Ffailing that was completely
OL,9,Fdevastating because your freedom gets
OL,10,Fripped away from you and you're so
OL,11,Fclose to it.
OL,13,F"It's probably going to take me
OL,14,Fanother six or seven months to get
OL,15,Fanother test and by the time I do,
OL,16,FI'll be 18 and doing my A-levels so
OL,17,Fit's not easy."
