OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FLee Dillon, MP for Newbury said: "In
OL,7,Fthe past few weeks, I've been
OL,8,Fcontacted by many learner drivers and
OL,9,Ftheir families in Newbury who are
OL,10,Fcaught in an endless and frustrating
OL,11,Fcycle - waiting for months, even close
OL,12,Fto a year, to secure a driving test.
OL,13,FThis delay is having a huge impact on
OL,14,Four community, leaving many without
OL,15,Fthe freedom and opportunities that
OL,16,Fcome with a driving licence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
