OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,F"Imagine being ready to take your
OL,7,Ftest, planning for the independence
OL,8,Fthat driving can bring - whether it's
OL,9,Ffor work, education, or simply gaining
OL,10,Ffreedom. Now imagine finding out that
OL,11,Fno test slots are available for
OL,12,Fmonths. In Newbury, the current wait
OL,13,Fis pushing 12 months for many learners.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
