OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,F"This issue isn't new. It's sadly been
OL,7,Fbuilding since the pandemic, but
OL,8,Frecent data shows that the situation
OL,9,Fhas only gotten worse. Nationally, the
OL,10,Faverage waiting time is now over 180
OL,11,Fdays. For rural areas like ours, where
OL,12,Fpublic transport options are limited,
OL,13,Fhaving a car is often essential for
OL,14,Fdaily life."
OL,16,FTo make matters worse, some third
OL,17,Fparties are exploiting the frantic
OL,18,Fhunt for tests by using bots to bulk
OL,19,Fbuy slots - charging up to #400 for
OL,20,Fthe privilege.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
