OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FTo beat the shortages, an increasing
OL,7,Fnumber of learners are taking matters
OL,8,Finto their own hands by booking tests
OL,9,Fin unfamiliar towns and cities.
OL,11,FDriving instructor Sue Smith said:
OL,12,F"People come from outside of Newbury
OL,13,Fand we can see how the tests are
OL,14,Fwasted because if you've got a learner
OL,15,Fthat has never been on a dual
OL,16,Fcarriageway let alone on a short entry
OL,17,Fone like in Newbury, it's dangerous
OL,18,Ffor the examiners, it's dangerous for
OL,19,Fthem and they are likely to fail."
