OL,3,CHow long is the wait at your local
OL,4,Cdriving test centre?
OL,6,FThe Driver and Vehicle Standards
OL,7,FAgency created almost 150,000 new test
OL,8,Fslots - providing a total of almost
OL,9,Ftwo million in the past year.
OL,11,FAs of September 2024, the average
OL,12,Fwaiting time was just over 18 weeks,
OL,13,Fonly slightly down on this time last
OL,14,Fyear when it was around 20 weeks.
OL,16,FThe DVSA says it continues to recruit
OL,17,Fmore examiners in a bid to increase
OL,18,Fthe number of tests available.
